column5: No backgrounds, no photoshop
Nice Rainbow! How do we know its you?  LOL
is this a report? if so wouldve been better with some info, j/k, i like that pic more
Nice rainbow.
Nice work fishfinder!  Great pic!  Keep em coming.  You are getting quite the reputation on here...wish I could land them like you do!
Now thats what Im talkin about !  Great shot .... next time dont forget we need GPS coords too
Beauty bow.  Keep 'em coming.
Attaboy, Fishfinder.  A very pretty fish.  Thanks for posting.
I don't like the camo... could you wear something frilly next time?  Beautiful fish and great pic!

I think he caught it in the woods because he is just covered with trees. Nice fish you got their. By the way what is that white stuff on the edge of the water we dont have that down here in the south?  Art
hey, i know that spot!
Beauty fish FF, congrats.
nice bow....thats better
WTG, nice looking bow!
FF NICE!!!! Dude beauty fish and an awesome pic to Boot!  Thanks for sharing man!  Gerritt.
A really nice fish for sure. I suspect that those are CC's hands though...and Nauti's coat.
Well, the picture is great.. still not the right species being held up though.
what an awesome looking fish!  Cheers!
Damn fine.
